# TypeScript Rules

Strict mode ON — `noUncheckedIndexedAccess`, `exactOptionalPropertyTypes`.

## Domain Types

```ts
type ArticleStatus = "draft" | "published" | "archived"
type ArticleId = string & { readonly brand: "ArticleId" }

interface Article {
  id: ArticleId
  title: string
  slug: string
  excerpt: string
  content: string
  status: ArticleStatus
  publishedAt: Date | null
  createdAt: Date
  updatedAt: Date
}

// ✅ Props eksplisit
interface ArticleFormProps {
  article?: Article
  onSuccess?: () => void
}

// ✅ unknown + validate, bukan any — terutama input form & API response
function parseArticleInput(raw: unknown): ArticleInput { ... }
```

## Naming
- Components → PascalCase file · Hooks → `useXxx.ts` · Utils → camelCase
- Constants → `SCREAMING_SNAKE` · Types → PascalCase
- Server Actions → verb + noun: `createArticle`, `updateArticle`, `deleteArticle`

## Validasi & Forms
- Zod schema di `lib/validations/` — validasi input artikel & form CMS
- React Hook Form + Zod untuk form CRUD
- Server state → TanStack Query (jika perlu client refetch), bukan Zustand
- Slug generation & sanitasi di `lib/` — bukan scattered di component
